Note: ============================================================================
Note: Fast Name-to-Number Lookup
Note: ============================================================================

Process called "get_darwin_x86_64_syscall_number" that takes name as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Returns the syscall number (with 0x2000000 prefix) for a given name on Darwin x86_64
    Note: Returns -1 if the syscall name is not recognized

    If StringCore.string_equals(name, "read") is equal to 1:
        Return SYS_DARWIN_X64_READ
    End If
    If StringCore.string_equals(name, "write") is equal to 1:
        Return SYS_DARWIN_X64_WRITE
